WEBVTT

00:00:35.900 --> 00:00:38.566
=Angels and Guards=

00:00:38.600 --> 00:00:41.266
=Episode 14=

00:01:03.066 --> 00:01:04.466
Not bad-looking.

00:01:11.566 --> 00:01:12.966
They all left.
Aren't you following them?

00:01:13.233 --> 00:01:14.100
Let them go.

00:01:15.333 --> 00:01:16.166
Today, I'm staying with you.

00:01:16.766 --> 00:01:17.700
Why are you staying with me?

00:01:19.266 --> 00:01:20.133
(Guan.)

00:01:20.900 --> 00:01:23.566
(Keep watch on Chong'er Pavilion
all day tomorrow.)

00:01:23.766 --> 00:01:24.533
(Watch Chang Beiming.)

00:01:24.933 --> 00:01:26.466
(Don't let him out of your sight.)

00:01:26.666 --> 00:01:27.433
(Not until I return.)

00:01:27.866 --> 00:01:29.766
(But what if he gets mad and hits me?)

00:01:30.100 --> 00:01:31.533
(I don't care how you do it,)

00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:33.166
(but you must keep him there for me.)

00:01:34.066 --> 00:01:36.000
(Guan, this mission is very important.)

00:01:36.500 --> 00:01:37.266
(Can you do it?)

00:01:38.100 --> 00:01:38.800
(If it is your order,)

00:01:39.600 --> 00:01:40.666
(I will see it through,
even if it kills me.)

00:01:41.433 --> 00:01:42.200
Don't worry about it.

00:01:43.233 --> 00:01:44.333
I'm not letting you out of my sight.

00:01:48.533 --> 00:01:49.700
Are you crazy?

00:01:50.333 --> 00:01:51.500
Say what you want.

00:01:51.733 --> 00:01:53.500
Whatever you do today, I do too.

00:02:25.000 --> 00:02:26.000
Sneaky.

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:34.233
You are not shaking me off today.

00:02:35.600 --> 00:02:36.766
Are you some kind of pervert?

00:02:36.766 --> 00:02:38.000
Why do you keep stalking me?

00:02:38.533 --> 00:02:39.866
Just following orders. Sorry.

00:02:41.000 --> 00:02:42.666
Will you follow me
to the bathroom too?

00:02:43.500 --> 00:02:44.066
If I have to.

00:02:46.400 --> 00:02:47.433
I'll beat you up.

00:02:47.566 --> 00:02:48.633
Beat me up. I still have to follow you.

00:02:53.333 --> 00:02:53.733
Fine.

00:02:54.333 --> 00:02:55.166
I'm going to play cards.

00:02:55.233 --> 00:02:56.766
Have fun standing guard outside.

00:02:57.533 --> 00:02:58.566
Chang Shuai. Close the door.

00:02:59.000 --> 00:02:59.600
Right away.

00:03:01.166 --> 00:03:02.366
Chang, you're back.

00:03:02.500 --> 00:03:02.900
Come on.

00:03:03.066 --> 00:03:03.466
Sit.

00:03:04.366 --> 00:03:04.933
What's going on?

00:03:06.000 --> 00:03:07.833
Bingfan must be out on a mission today

00:03:08.266 --> 00:03:09.433
and sent that guy to watch over me.

00:03:10.033 --> 00:03:10.366
What?

00:03:10.700 --> 00:03:11.733
Who does he think he is?

00:03:12.033 --> 00:03:12.566
I'll deal with him.

00:03:12.866 --> 00:03:13.366
Forget him.

00:03:13.700 --> 00:03:14.300
Cards.

00:03:14.600 --> 00:03:16.166
We'll play all night.

00:03:16.500 --> 00:03:17.533
Let's see who wears out first.

00:03:17.700 --> 00:03:18.700
Come on.

00:03:19.333 --> 00:03:19.933
Shuffle.

00:03:20.200 --> 00:03:21.200
Bring some sunflower seeds.

00:03:42.833 --> 00:03:45.533
Mr. Lu, don't you bow before me?

00:03:47.000 --> 00:03:47.666
Greetings, Your Highness.

00:03:48.200 --> 00:03:49.266
Greetings, Your Highness.

00:03:52.233 --> 00:03:52.900
Mr. Lu.

00:03:53.500 --> 00:03:54.566
The Dragon-Phoenix Jade.

00:03:54.666 --> 00:03:55.733
Is it safe?

00:03:57.000 --> 00:03:58.000
Rest assured, Your Highness.

00:03:58.233 --> 00:03:59.800
I have it on me.

00:04:00.266 --> 00:04:01.300
There is nothing to worry about.

00:04:03.500 --> 00:04:04.233
By the way, Your Highness,

00:04:05.033 --> 00:04:06.300
the banquet has ended.

00:04:06.666 --> 00:04:07.666
It's late.

00:04:08.000 --> 00:04:09.666
Why are you out here alone?

00:04:10.333 --> 00:04:11.233
Where are your maids?

00:04:16.000 --> 00:04:16.766
Mr. Lu.

00:04:22.033 --> 00:04:22.600
What?

00:04:22.900 --> 00:04:24.466
Red Dust Reverie! Hold your breath!

00:04:49.000 --> 00:04:49.533
Excellent wine.

00:04:49.933 --> 00:04:50.366
It is.

00:04:51.533 --> 00:04:52.066
Constable Guan.

00:04:52.566 --> 00:04:53.100
Getting tired?

00:04:55.366 --> 00:04:55.800
Constable Guan!

00:04:56.000 --> 00:04:56.533
Where is he?

00:04:57.200 --> 00:04:58.966
Young Master Chang lost, sulked,
and drank too much.

00:04:59.266 --> 00:05:00.033
He passed out over there.

00:05:00.200 --> 00:05:00.600
Yeah.

00:05:05.333 --> 00:05:05.866
Guan.

00:05:06.166 --> 00:05:07.033
Join us for a few hands.

00:05:08.500 --> 00:05:09.266
I don't know how to play.

00:05:09.533 --> 00:05:10.200
Then drink with us.

00:05:10.400 --> 00:05:11.400
Right.

00:05:11.600 --> 00:05:12.500
Come drink with us.

00:05:13.033 --> 00:05:14.133
Beiming is asleep anyway.

00:05:14.566 --> 00:05:15.233
You can keep us company.

00:05:15.433 --> 00:05:16.700
You three are men of high status.

00:05:17.366 --> 00:05:18.466
I would not presume to drink with you.

00:05:19.433 --> 00:05:20.200
Too good to drink with us?

00:05:20.600 --> 00:05:21.300
No, no.

00:05:21.900 --> 00:05:22.833
I really am on duty.

00:05:23.333 --> 00:05:23.833
Guan.

00:05:24.233 --> 00:05:25.133
Just sit here.

00:05:25.766 --> 00:05:27.000
You're only here

00:05:27.033 --> 00:05:28.300
to watch Chang Beiming
for Miss Shen, right?

00:05:28.833 --> 00:05:30.766
Sit with us. We can drink

00:05:31.266 --> 00:05:32.133
and watch him at the same time.

00:05:32.566 --> 00:05:33.500
Where can he go?

00:05:34.400 --> 00:05:34.766
Well...

00:05:35.366 --> 00:05:35.633
All right.

00:05:37.033 --> 00:05:37.566
Drink.

00:05:37.833 --> 00:05:38.400
Constable Guan.

00:05:39.733 --> 00:05:40.333
Fill it up.

00:05:41.533 --> 00:05:42.433
(The banquet just ended.)

00:05:43.033 --> 00:05:44.433
(How is the princess already gone?)

00:05:51.833 --> 00:05:52.333
Your Highness.

00:05:53.600 --> 00:05:54.633
(Princess Pingyang)
They knocked me out

00:05:54.666 --> 00:05:56.100
and locked me in the woodshed.

00:05:57.366 --> 00:05:57.866
Oh no!

00:06:04.033 --> 00:06:04.400
Gosh!

00:06:05.100 --> 00:06:05.966
Your Highness, hide.

00:06:13.700 --> 00:06:14.300
Feng Fuliu.

00:06:18.400 --> 00:06:18.966
Feng Fuliu.

00:06:19.700 --> 00:06:20.766
Nowhere left to run.

00:06:21.166 --> 00:06:22.233
We knew you had tricks,

00:06:22.500 --> 00:06:24.333
so we posted archers in advance.

00:06:26.366 --> 00:06:26.933
Hero Feng,

00:06:27.233 --> 00:06:28.666
just give it back.

00:06:28.900 --> 00:06:30.133
You might still get leniency.

00:06:31.600 --> 00:06:32.600
You are so kind.

00:06:35.500 --> 00:06:36.066
See you next time.

00:06:43.600 --> 00:06:44.700
Go protect the princess.

00:06:44.866 --> 00:06:45.266
Go!

00:07:03.433 --> 00:07:03.966
Bingfan.

00:07:32.033 --> 00:07:32.766
(Feng Fuliu.)

00:07:33.566 --> 00:07:34.633
(He is out cold too.)

00:07:58.100 --> 00:07:59.466
Taking advantage while I'm down?

00:08:04.533 --> 00:08:05.233
Who are you?

00:08:07.500 --> 00:08:08.366
Who else?

00:08:09.033 --> 00:08:09.800
I'm Feng Fuliu.

00:08:10.233 --> 00:08:11.300
Chang Beiming, stop pretending.

00:08:11.866 --> 00:08:13.066
I haven't known many men.

00:08:13.333 --> 00:08:14.666
But I know your scent too well.

00:08:15.166 --> 00:08:16.066
Who are you really?

00:08:16.766 --> 00:08:17.766
Who is Chang Beiming?

00:08:18.766 --> 00:08:19.433
Could he be

00:08:20.166 --> 00:08:21.066
your sweetheart?

00:08:21.266 --> 00:08:22.466
Take off the mask if you dare.

00:08:23.333 --> 00:08:25.366
My face is hideous.
I might scare you.

00:08:25.700 --> 00:08:26.800
What are you after?

00:08:29.333 --> 00:08:30.766
What if...

00:08:34.866 --> 00:08:36.233
I like you.

00:08:39.100 --> 00:08:39.766
What did you say?

00:08:40.733 --> 00:08:41.333
I said

00:08:42.700 --> 00:08:43.900
I liked you

00:08:45.000 --> 00:08:46.000
from the moment I first saw you.

00:09:00.733 --> 00:09:01.333
Shameless.

00:09:01.733 --> 00:09:02.266
Scoundrel.

00:09:03.366 --> 00:09:05.433
If liking you makes me shameless,

00:09:05.600 --> 00:09:06.666
then I'll gladly be a scoundrel.

00:09:08.700 --> 00:09:09.433
Be serious.

00:09:09.700 --> 00:09:10.733
I am serious.

00:09:11.500 --> 00:09:12.000
And

00:09:12.766 --> 00:09:13.833
I mean every word.

00:09:15.733 --> 00:09:16.800
You are not allowed to like me.

00:09:18.600 --> 00:09:19.266
Why?

00:09:20.400 --> 00:09:21.400
Is your heart

00:09:23.066 --> 00:09:24.100
already taken?

00:09:25.866 --> 00:09:26.533
None of your business.

00:09:39.433 --> 00:09:40.333
How long will you keep this up?

00:09:40.600 --> 00:09:41.800
Until I bring you in.

00:09:48.700 --> 00:09:49.600
What trick is this now?

00:09:54.433 --> 00:09:55.166
A Bloodred Centipede!

00:09:57.100 --> 00:09:58.466
Hold on. I'll get you out.

00:10:12.566 --> 00:10:13.100
Mr. Lu.

00:10:14.166 --> 00:10:14.566
Mr. Lu.

00:10:17.600 --> 00:10:18.200
Mr. Lu.

00:10:19.600 --> 00:10:19.866
Feng...

00:10:21.933 --> 00:10:22.366
How dare you!

00:10:22.866 --> 00:10:24.200
You see me and don't bow?

00:10:30.533 --> 00:10:31.266
Forgive me, Your Highness.

00:10:32.700 --> 00:10:33.366
Mr. Lu.

00:10:33.866 --> 00:10:35.233
The Dragon-Phoenix Jade is gone.

00:10:35.500 --> 00:10:37.100
Is this how you serve the court?

00:10:37.866 --> 00:10:38.200
I...

00:10:41.733 --> 00:10:42.133
Guards!

00:10:42.366 --> 00:10:44.033
Take Hua Mange and Cheng Xintian
into custody.

00:10:44.233 --> 00:10:44.633
Yes, my lord.

00:10:45.366 --> 00:10:45.633
What?

00:10:46.733 --> 00:10:47.233
Mr. Lu.

00:10:47.900 --> 00:10:49.900
Why are you arresting us?

00:10:50.600 --> 00:10:53.100
The three of you were
to protect the princess.

00:10:53.433 --> 00:10:56.033
Because of your incompetence,
the Jade was stolen on my watch.

00:10:56.566 --> 00:10:57.400
What punishment do you deserve?

00:11:00.566 --> 00:11:01.433
Mr. Lu.

00:11:01.933 --> 00:11:03.200
The way you pin the blame on others

00:11:03.233 --> 00:11:04.666
is truly effortless.

00:11:55.166 --> 00:11:56.333
I'll find some herbs nearby

00:11:56.733 --> 00:11:57.433
and start a fire

00:11:58.066 --> 00:11:58.966
to clean the wound
and reduce the swelling.

00:12:00.100 --> 00:12:00.866
Don't go.

00:12:02.166 --> 00:12:03.600
I'll stay close.
I will be right back.

00:12:11.433 --> 00:12:12.133
What are you doing?

00:12:13.600 --> 00:12:15.666
I will bring you in,
even if it kills me.

00:12:19.933 --> 00:12:21.300
You would risk your life
just to catch me?

00:12:58.766 --> 00:13:04.400
♪Lost too deep in the haze,
my eyes turn red♪

00:13:05.000 --> 00:13:10.500
♪Your scent remains
and walks with me♪

00:13:11.266 --> 00:13:16.500
♪I follow the wind,
rushing toward you♪

00:13:17.200 --> 00:13:22.066
♪Drowning in your world♪

00:13:22.966 --> 00:13:28.733
♪I ask myself before I can wake♪

00:13:29.266 --> 00:13:34.833
♪I only remember why my heart
first raced for you♪

00:13:35.166 --> 00:13:40.400
♪If fate says I must walk alone♪

00:13:41.400 --> 00:13:46.766
♪If love could wake me for you♪

00:13:47.100 --> 00:13:52.166
♪I loved you and forgot myself♪

00:13:52.866 --> 00:13:58.666
♪Lost in love, I forgot myself♪

00:13:59.200 --> 00:14:03.633
♪Was I not trying hard enough♪

00:14:05.133 --> 00:14:10.566
♪Why did fate make me fall for you♪

00:14:11.366 --> 00:14:16.533
♪Yet forget to warn my heart♪

00:14:17.133 --> 00:14:22.633
♪If fate leaves me to walk alone♪

00:14:23.466 --> 00:14:28.900
♪Why did it let me meet you first♪

00:14:28.900 --> 00:14:31.900
♪Was it me♪

00:14:32.033 --> 00:14:35.133
♪Not trying hard enough to run to you♪

00:14:35.400 --> 00:14:40.766
♪Unable to touch you,
so far out of reach♪

00:14:40.800 --> 00:14:46.600
♪If fate leaves me to walk alone♪

00:14:47.533 --> 00:14:52.833
♪Why did it let me meet you first♪

00:14:52.866 --> 00:14:55.666
♪Was it me♪

00:14:56.300 --> 00:14:58.866
♪Not trying hard enough♪

00:14:59.266 --> 00:15:04.666
♪To hold on to who you were♪

00:15:05.000 --> 00:15:10.866
♪If fate leaves me to walk alone♪

00:15:11.600 --> 00:15:16.200
♪I loved you until I lost myself♪

00:15:16.466 --> 00:15:22.833
♪If fate is bound to move on♪

00:15:23.200 --> 00:15:31.433
♪Let me meet the old you once again♪

00:16:07.566 --> 00:16:07.966
Bingfan.

00:16:09.666 --> 00:16:10.133
Bingfan.

00:16:18.600 --> 00:16:20.133
Are you out of your mind?

00:16:20.733 --> 00:16:21.800
You really are Feng Fuliu.

00:16:22.366 --> 00:16:24.200
You lied to me
and took liberties with me.

00:16:26.266 --> 00:16:27.966
Look around. Where are you?

00:16:42.733 --> 00:16:43.666
Chong'er Pavilion?

00:16:45.066 --> 00:16:46.433
How did I end up back here?

00:17:01.433 --> 00:17:02.200
Sorry.

00:17:08.500 --> 00:17:09.766
Next time you hit someone,

00:17:10.866 --> 00:17:11.900
look first.

00:17:15.833 --> 00:17:17.733
But why was I sleeping
at Chong'er Pavilion?

00:17:20.233 --> 00:17:21.333
I clearly remember

00:17:21.866 --> 00:17:24.033
being in some ruins with Feng Fuliu.

00:17:24.933 --> 00:17:25.700
And...

00:17:26.533 --> 00:17:28.066
I cuffed him.

00:17:29.700 --> 00:17:30.400
Where are my handcuffs?

00:17:37.500 --> 00:17:38.500
Why are they here?

00:17:42.500 --> 00:17:44.400
Guan Yunfeng gave me these.

00:17:44.533 --> 00:17:46.266
Custom-made steel handcuffs.

00:17:47.866 --> 00:17:49.566
Feng Fuliu couldn't have had the key.

00:18:03.500 --> 00:18:05.066
Chang Beiming.

00:18:07.500 --> 00:18:08.933
You are Feng Fuliu, aren't you?

00:18:10.066 --> 00:18:10.566
(Feng Fuliu.)

00:18:13.033 --> 00:18:13.966
(Who exactly are you?)

00:18:14.500 --> 00:18:16.100
(Chang Beiming, who exactly are you?)

00:18:18.400 --> 00:18:19.266
(Who are you?)

00:18:22.166 --> 00:18:23.166
(You know martial arts?)

00:18:24.900 --> 00:18:25.800
(Who are you?)

00:18:27.433 --> 00:18:28.133
(Who are you?)

00:18:30.433 --> 00:18:31.966
You are Feng Fuliu.

00:18:49.233 --> 00:18:52.400
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

00:18:52.766 --> 00:18:56.133
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

00:18:56.400 --> 00:18:59.400
♪My heart drifted lost♪

00:18:59.400 --> 00:19:02.800
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

00:19:03.900 --> 00:19:07.100
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

00:19:07.533 --> 00:19:10.866
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

00:19:11.433 --> 00:19:13.633
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

00:19:13.633 --> 00:19:17.666
♪I've softly let it go♪

00:19:17.700 --> 00:19:21.566
♪The vow you made was true♪

00:19:21.566 --> 00:19:25.300
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

00:19:25.600 --> 00:19:27.500
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

00:19:27.533 --> 00:19:32.066
♪And forget at world's end♪

00:19:32.366 --> 00:19:33.866
♪Embracing memory♪

00:19:33.866 --> 00:19:36.233
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

00:19:36.233 --> 00:19:40.100
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

00:19:40.100 --> 00:19:42.400
♪I wish to let it pass♪

00:19:42.433 --> 00:19:47.433
♪And run toward this vast life♪